data.description: Embrace the perfect blend of convenience and charm in this 2-bed, 1-bath  gem. Ideal location near highways, shopping, and dining. Features a spacious interior, 2021 roof, and all-new impact windows. The allure of this home extends outdoors to a vast screened yard, with room for a pool, perfect for entertaining or simply unwinding amidst the lush greenery or easily converted into a 3 bed. Embrace the joys of gardening in your expansive garden, surrounded by an abundance of trees, including three prolific mango trees that generously bear fruit during the summer months.No HOA or rental restrictions. Live the South Florida lifestyle to the fullest in this centrally located haven. Act fast, as this gem won't last!
